logicalExpression.expressionTemplate: CASE %1 WHEN '890' THEN 'Service' WHEN '999' THEN 'FDM-Service' WHEN '400' THEN 'MB - Systems' WHEN '410' THEN 'MB - Systems' WHEN '430' THEN 'MB - SP' WHEN '470' THEN 'MB - Consumables' WHEN '393' THEN 'FDM-Maintenance and SP' WHEN '392' THEN 'FDM-Maintenance and SP' WHEN '398' THEN 'Customer Support' WHEN '394' THEN 'Customer Support' ELSE  CASE  WHEN  CAST (%1 AS DOUBLE PRECISION ) BETWEEN 101 AND 189 THEN 'Equipment' WHEN  CAST (%1 AS DOUBLE PRECISION ) BETWEEN 191 AND 199 THEN 'Equipment Other' WHEN  CAST (%1 AS DOUBLE PRECISION ) BETWEEN 201 AND 271 THEN 'FDM-Equipment' WHEN  CAST (%1 AS DOUBLE PRECISION ) BETWEEN 272 AND 299 THEN 'FDM-Equipment Other' ELSE  CASE  LEFT(%1, 1) WHEN '5' THEN 'Resins' WHEN '6' THEN 'Resins' WHEN '7' THEN 'FDM-Consumable' WHEN '8' THEN 'Service' WHEN '9' THEN 'FDM-Service' ELSE  CASE  WHEN %2 = 'FRT' THEN 'Freight' ELSE 'Other' END  END  END  END
